<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 14:04:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>六次重大失败导致一分：垮台 vs 哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/six-significant-failures-that-lead-to-one-point-collapse-vs-hamas/0000018b-0f15-dfff-a7eb-afdd0bb80000</link><description>以色列事先没有收到关于入侵的情报警告，即使在入侵开始后，现场也没有足够的可用部队到达遭受攻击的地点。即使在部队涌入该地区后，包括精锐部队在内的许多部队仍然在集结点等待了很长时间，而不是被派往现场。这是六个主要的失败。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 13:49:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/six-significant-failures-that-lead-to-one-point-collapse-vs-hamas/0000018b-0f15-dfff-a7eb-afdd0bb80000</guid></item><item><title>问答：以色列遭遇火箭弹袭击或恐怖袭击时我该怎么办？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/q-a-what-should-i-do-during-a-rocket-strike-in-israel/0000018b-0f27-dcc2-a99b-1f37cbe80000</link><description>加沙火箭袭击期间住在哪里最安全？我可以离开这个国家吗？如何找到失踪人员？是否有英语求助热线？</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 12:54:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/q-a-what-should-i-do-during-a-rocket-strike-in-israel/0000018b-0f27-dcc2-a99b-1f37cbe80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列死亡：平民、士兵和紧急服务人员在与哈马斯的战争中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/israels-dead-civilians-soldiers-emergency-services-personnel-killed-in-war-with-hamas/0000018b-0de8-dc5d-a39f-9fecb5a30000</link><description>哈马斯对以色列南部发动突然袭击，造成至少 600 名以色列公民、士兵、警察和消防员死亡。此列表将持续更新</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 12:10:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/israels-dead-civilians-soldiers-emergency-services-personnel-killed-in-war-with-hamas/0000018b-0de8-dc5d-a39f-9fecb5a30000</guid></item><item><title>“恐怖主义没有任何理由”：世界对哈马斯对以色列的致命袭击作出反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/no-justification-for-terrorism-world-reacts-to-hamas-deadly-attack-on-israel/0000018b-0e9f-dae3-a1cb-bf9f532b0000</link><description>当以色列公民与从加沙渗透的巴勒斯坦恐怖分子作战时，国际社会大多数声音谴责对以色列平民的袭击，并敦促停止敌对行动</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 11:19:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/no-justification-for-terrorism-world-reacts-to-hamas-deadly-attack-on-israel/0000018b-0e9f-dae3-a1cb-bf9f532b0000</guid></item><item><title>警察在亚历山大旅游景点杀死 2 名以色列人和 1 名埃及人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/policeman-kills-2-israelis-1-egyptian-at-tourist-site-in-alexandria/0000018b-0eaf-dae3-a1cb-bfaf45830000</link><description>埃及发生袭击事件的消息传出，埃及的反以色列情绪在暴力事件期间尤其高涨，而以色列在从加沙发动大规模入侵后与巴勒斯坦武装分子作战之际传出袭击事件的消息。</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 10:11:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/policeman-kills-2-israelis-1-egyptian-at-tourist-site-in-alexandria/0000018b-0eaf-dae3-a1cb-bfaf45830000</guid></item><item><title>加沙边境附近被围困基布兹的居民：“我们没有物资”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-besieged-kibbutz-near-gaza-border-we-have-no-supplies/0000018b-0e90-dc5d-a39f-9ef42a130000</link><description>当以色列士兵在基布兹扫荡恐怖分子时，卡法阿扎一半以上的居民仍被困在安全室里</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 09:59:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-besieged-kibbutz-near-gaza-border-we-have-no-supplies/0000018b-0e90-dc5d-a39f-9ef42a130000</guid></item><item><title>真主党向以色列发射迫击炮弹，建议居民向南撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-launches-mortar-shells-at-israel-residents-advised-to-evacuate-southwards/0000018b-0e2a-dc5d-a39f-9e6e79930000</link><description>真主党增加北部战线攻击以色列，并祝贺哈马斯。联合国呼吁双方停止事态升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 08:27:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-launches-mortar-shells-at-israel-residents-advised-to-evacuate-southwards/0000018b-0e2a-dc5d-a39f-9e6e79930000</guid></item><item><title>这对以色列来说是一场灾难。但这不是另一场赎罪日战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/this-is-a-catastrophe-for-israel-but-its-not-another-yom-kippur-war/0000018b-0e41-d8fc-adff-6f6dbc000000</link><description>最初的赎罪日战争与本周哈马斯突然发生的创伤性袭击之间的对比是显而易见且引人注目的。但有一个关键的区别——这将决定这场战争如何结束</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 08:25:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/this-is-a-catastrophe-for-israel-but-its-not-another-yom-kippur-war/0000018b-0e41-d8fc-adff-6f6dbc000000</guid></item><item><title>加沙报告313人死亡，以军空袭高楼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/gaza-reports-313-dead-israeli-army-strikes-high-rises/0000018b-0e41-dae3-a1cb-bf4933a30000</link><description>加沙的目击者向《国土报》描述了相对空旷的街道，这与周六公开表示的支持形成鲜明对比</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 07:53:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article/.premium/gaza-reports-313-dead-israeli-army-strikes-high-rises/0000018b-0e41-dae3-a1cb-bf4933a30000</guid></item><item><title>突如其来的渗透造成至少 600 名以色列人死亡、2,000 人受伤，大规模的炮火震撼了以色列；加沙平民和士兵被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-live/over-250-israelis-killed-1-590-wounded-civilians-and-soldiers-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018b-0cd2-d8fc-adff-6dfe855e0000</link><description>数十名巴勒斯坦武装分子从加沙经陆海空渗透以色列 ■ 约2,500 枚火箭弹从加沙地带发射 ■ 至少600 名以色列人死亡，2,000 多人受伤 ■ 军队袭击加沙哈马斯目标；据报道，256 名巴勒斯坦人被杀 ■ “大量”平民和士兵在加沙被扣为人质</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 03:09:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-08/ty-article-l